</span>                            <span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">f</span><span class="sh">"</span><span class="s">Enter the </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">game</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">num</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s"> digits(inputNum): </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">guess</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="sh">"</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># 사용자가 입력한 추측값을 콘솔에 출력함 
