</span>                <span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sh">"</span><span class="s">Invalid input.</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="sh">"</span><span class="p">)</span>  <span class="c1"># 에러 메시지를 콘솔에 출력
